Weymouth_Town.Russell M. Dicey House: The Russell M. Dicey House is a historic house at 56 Pope Street in Quincy, Massachusetts. The 1-1/2 story wood frame house was built in 1918, and is a well-preserved example of a modest Craftsman bungalow. It has the extended eaves with brackets typical of the style, as well as a fieldstone porch with tapered square posts.
